119
00:06:57,251 --> 00:07:00,669
Whoo-hoo-hoo! Whoo!

120
00:07:02,306 --> 00:07:04,923
<i>♪ I need a hero ♪</i>

121
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,517
Yeah! Hah!

122
00:07:26,563 --> 00:07:29,043
This makes things
a whole lot better.

123
00:07:32,619 --> 00:07:35,036
Mother of God!

124
