you tell them you saw a woman,
and she ran that way.

125
00:07:40,043 --> 00:07:43,211
You're cool, guys.
Stay true to yourselves.

126
00:07:43,246 --> 00:07:45,130
What an idiot.

127
00:07:45,182 --> 00:07:48,683
<i>I don't remember
how I got back to the city,</i>

128
00:07:48,719 --> 00:07:51,603
<i>but I know I got mugged.</i>

129
