150
00:08:43,490 --> 00:08:46,074
I don't want to blame Mike
for letting me use his boat,

151
00:08:46,109 --> 00:08:48,577
but I will say that he didn't
show the best judgment either.

152
00:08:48,612 --> 00:08:52,113
- Then there's my mom,
- You're deflecting, man.

153
00:08:52,148 --> 00:08:54,449
Hey, come on,
no cross talk.

154
00:08:54,484 --> 00:08:57,335
Some might call it deflecting,
some might call it fact.

155
00:08:57,371 --> 00:08:59,538
I've identified
the enemy, details.

156
00:09:01,375 --> 00:09:04,759
I'm sorry. If everybody's gonna
get a chance to share tonight,

157
00:09:04,795 --> 00:09:06,795
