what I wanted to say.

159
00:09:10,267 --> 00:09:13,635
What do you want to say?

160
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:15,053
Isn't it hot in here?

161
00:09:15,105 --> 00:09:16,671
What do you say we vote
to turn down the heat?

162
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:19,107
Please. Just hurry up,
finish your share.

163
00:09:19,142 --> 00:09:21,120
But I can't with
all this pressure!

164
00:09:21,144 --> 00:09:22,561
Then shut the fuck up!

165
00:09:22,613 --> 00:09:24,529
Hey, come on! No acting out!

166
00:09:24,565 --> 00:09:27,649
Well, then tell this asshole
to shut the fuck up

167
00:09:27,684 --> 00:09:30,068
and let somebody else speak!

168
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:33,354
I am detoxifying here, man!

169
00:09:33,373 --> 00:09:40,579
And what he's saying,
he's got me so confused
I think I'm gonna fucking snap!

170
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:45,800
Thanks for letting me share.

171
00:09:47,638 --> 00:09:50,538
Hi. My name is Jeff,
and I'm an alcoholic.

172
00:09:50,557 --> 00:09:52,641
Hi, Jeff.

173
00:09:52,676 --> 00:09:54,404
What I've been
trying to say...

174
00:09:54,428 --> 00:09:58,430
is that I don't want to
blame it on the program.

175
00:09:58,482 --> 00:10:01,549
But I've spent almost a decade

176
00:10:01,568 --> 00:10:05,153
thinking that the most
important thing in my life
is staying sober

177
00:10:05,188 --> 00:10:09,274
while everyone else I know has
gone on to do great things
with their lives.

178
00:10:09,326 --> 00:10:13,161
And all I do is sneak into
gyms and substitute teach
on the side,

179
00:10:13,196 --> 00:10:14,395
not that I'm bad at it.

180
00:10:14,414 --> 00:10:17,565
I'm actually pretty good.

181
00:10:17,584 --> 00:10:20,285
<i>I just don't find it
fulfilling.</i>

182
00:10:30,464 --> 00:10:32,714
All right!
Fuck geography!

183
00:10:32,749 --> 00:10:36,250
Let's play Simon says!
Simon says do this!

184
00:10:36,269 --> 00:10:39,187
I... love... school!

185
00:10:39,222 --> 00:10:42,140
Books... are... good!

186
00:10:42,192 --> 00:10:44,693
Reading... is... good!

187
00:10:44,728 --> 00:10:48,563
You! You, you're out,
you're out. Seriously.

188
00:10:53,370 --> 00:10:56,287
I'm...

189
