for over a week now.

194
00:11:11,638 --> 00:11:14,172
I think at the Serene Horizon
meeting on Thursday

195
00:11:14,224 --> 00:11:17,475
I'm just going to have
to cut Lenny loose.

196
00:11:17,511 --> 00:11:20,795
I know I should be trying
to help him for my benefit
as well as his,

197
00:11:20,814 --> 00:11:25,466
but I just don't have
the strength right now.

198
00:11:25,485 --> 00:11:27,736
You see,
my Tourette's Syndrome

199
00:11:27,771 --> 00:11:32,323
