in my head.</i>

202
00:11:49,710 --> 00:11:53,628
This ain't no game, man!

203
00:11:53,663 --> 00:11:57,632
That's a foul!

204
00:11:57,667 --> 00:11:59,551
I love you, Jeff!

205
00:12:02,973 --> 00:12:05,774
Pushing!

206
00:12:05,809 --> 00:12:07,442
What?

207
00:12:07,477 --> 00:12:08,977
<i>It's debilitating.</i>

208
00:12:09,012 --> 00:12:11,646
What? That's not a foul!

209
00:12:11,681 --> 00:12:13,732
I'll show you a foul!

210
00:12:13,784 --> 00:12:15,467
I'll fuckin' kill you, Ref!

211
00:12:15,502 --> 00:12:17,702
Hoo! You're out of here!

212
00:12:17,738 --> 00:12:20,405
Oh, my God!
They're clearing the benches!

213
00:12:24,027 --> 00:12:27,462
Motherfucker, I told you
to quit clapping!

214
00:12:27,497 --> 00:12:30,715
Sorry. I'll turn
the TV down.

215
00:12:39,493 --> 00:12:40,925
<i>Since I was very young,</i>

216
00:12:40,977 --> 00:12:43,511
<i>I've always had
the same dream.</i>

217
00:12:44,931 --> 00:12:48,600
<i>Jeff? Jeff?</i>

218
00:12:48,652 --> 00:12:50,384
<i>Yes, you.</i>

219
00:12:50,403 --> 00:12:54,739
<i>Your job is to put
the red balls in the red bin</i>

220
00:12:54,775 --> 00:12:58,243
<i>and to put the yellow balls
