222
00:13:01,998 --> 00:13:03,248
<i>Got it?</i>

223
00:13:03,283 --> 00:13:05,333
- Yup.
- <i>Good.</i>

224
00:13:17,347 --> 00:13:19,347
<i>Yay, Jeff!</i>

225
00:13:19,382 --> 00:13:21,049
<i>Good!</i>

226
00:13:23,303 --> 00:13:26,054
<i>Good job, sweetie!</i>

227
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,524
