229
00:13:31,511 --> 00:13:33,945
<i>And all the details go away.</i>

230
00:13:33,980 --> 00:13:35,897
<i>It comforts me.</i>

231
00:13:35,932 --> 00:13:37,732
Thanks for letting me share.

232
00:13:37,767 --> 00:13:40,652
- Thanks, Jeff.
- Thanks, Jeff.

233
00:13:40,704 --> 00:13:42,381
That was
a great share, Jeff.

234
00:13:42,405 --> 00:13:45,456
So your message is
just to keep it simple?

235
00:13:45,492 --> 00:13:47,492
Yeah.

236
00:13:47,544 --> 00:13:51,496
