Serene Horizon meeting?
Did you share?

237
00:13:51,548 --> 00:13:54,644
Yeah, I shared.
Jeff, weren't you
listening?

238
00:13:54,668 --> 00:13:58,786
Yeah, I was.
How you doing, man?

239
00:13:58,805 --> 00:14:00,733
Well, it's been tough
this past two weeks,

240
00:14:00,757 --> 00:14:03,675
not drinking and losing
my job over at Con-Ed

241
00:14:03,727 --> 00:14:04,937
'cause I really
loved that.

242
00:14:04,961 --> 00:14:06,823
It's the only thing
I cared about.

243
00:14:06,847 --> 00:14:08,930
And I'm lonely.

244
00:14:08,965 --> 00:14:12,350
